__ Cantrip: Vandalize ________________________ Cost: 5 ______________________

Use:  cantrip vandalize < monster >            Material Component: monster
Use:  C vandalize < monster >

The cantrip vandalize is a minor magic of the spheres of alteration and 
enchantment.  When cast, the vandalize cantrip leaves a message hanging
in the air for all to see.  Pets may also be vandalized.  A good way to
leave your mark!
